node.text:
🔥 PEDAL TO THE METAL 🔥
Grind through the Pacific Northwest with @8ballr, @davidgravette, @smokeeyes & a heavy crew in PEDAL TO THE METAL Raw Mayhem 2017 trip! 💥 Link in Bio for more!
📹: @danstolling
🎬: @codylonglens
#IndependentTrucks #RideTheBest #BuiltToGrind
